Alumni Details >>
A Global Community of Innovators, Engineers, and Leaders
Netaji Subhas University of Technology (NSUT), Delhi, is proud of its expansive and accomplished alumni network, comprising tens of thousands of graduates across the world. From Australia to North America, NSUT alumni can be found in leading global corporations, research institutions, and innovation-driven organizations.
Our alumni actively contribute as mentors and advisors, and consistently encourage organizations to recruit NSUT students for internships and long-term professional roles.

Where Our Alumni Work
NSUT alumni are employed across a wide range of top-tier global organizations in the technology and engineering sectors.
Thousands of alumni employed as global technology leaders in software, cloud, and product-based companies (Google, Amazon, Microsoft, Adobe, etc.)


Alumni also contribute to major e-commerce firms, enterprise software organizations, research labs, startups, and professional associations.


Our alumni maintain a strong presence in both industry and academia, this reflects the versatility and depth of our educational foundation.


This widespread representation highlights the trust global employers place in NSUT graduates.

Global Reach and Presence
NSUT’s alumni network has a strong international footprint, while maintaining a substantial base in India.
Thousands of alumni reside across India, dominating its major metropolitan regions and technology hubs.


Thousands of graduates are employed internationally, including North America and other global innovation centers.


Our diverse network enables global collaboration, international career mobility, and a strong worldwide alumni presence.

Professional Domains and Career Paths
NSUT alumni work across a broad spectrum of professional roles, with a particularly strong representation in:
Engineering and Technology


Business Development and Strategy


Operations and Technical Management


Information Technology and Systems


Research and Advanced Technical Roles


The diversity of career paths underscores the adaptability of NSUT graduates and their ability to excel in both technical and leadership-oriented roles.

Academic Backgrounds
The academic profiles of NSUT alumni reflect the university’s multidisciplinary strength and technical depth.
Our alumni hold degrees in Computer Science and Engineering, Electrical, Electronics, and Communication Engineering in both bachelors and masters programs.


A significant number of our graduates go on to pursue master’s degrees in science, technology, engineering, and business management at Stanford, MIT, IIT-B and other renowned institutions, further strengthening NSUT’s academic and professional presence.




